WEBVTT

1
01:33:10.680 --> 01:33:12.180 
是在那之后，我被征召以后
After that, when I was drafted.

2
01:33:12.180 --> 01:33:13.180 
啊哈！盖世太保啊
Aha! Gestapo.

3
01:33:13.180 --> 01:33:14.780 
不不，是党卫军
No, no. S.S.

4
01:33:14.780 --> 01:33:16.720 
闭上你的嘴，白痴
Halten Sie doch den Mund, Idiot.

5
01:33:16.720 --> 01:33:18.320 
哦，中尉先生
Well, Herr Oberleutnant...

6
01:33:18.320 --> 01:33:20.480 
我还能为您做什么吗？
is there anything else I can do for you?

7
01:33:21.890 --> 01:33:24.390 
不了，谢谢，我已采访完毕
No, thank you. I have all the facts.

8
01:33:24.390 --> 01:33:25.390 
国际知名的
Union between two...

9
01:33:25.390 --> 01:33:26.990 
哈泽汀家族和
internationally prominent families

10
01:33:26.990 --> 01:33:28.860 
冯·德罗斯特·斯卡滕博格家族的结合
the Hazeltines and the von Droste

11
01:33:28.860 --> 01:33:30.160 
年度社交盛事
The social event of the year.

12
01:33:30.160 --> 01:33:31.630 
内容将在今天下午的报纸登出
It will be in the afternoon paper.

13
01:33:31.630 --> 01:33:32.970 
最好是这样
It had better be.

14
01:33:32.970 --> 01:33:34.970 
- 再见  - 祝您成功
- Auf Wiedersehen.  - Sieg heil.

15
01:33:34.970 --> 01:33:35.970 
至于你，施莱默
As for you, Schlemmer...

16
01:33:35.970 --> 01:33:37.840 
[SS既是党卫军亦是减薪的缩写]你又做回SS了…减薪
you're back in the S.S. Smaller salary.

17
01:33:37.840 --> 01:33:38.970 
先生，我要解释一下
Sir, let me explain.

18
01:33:38.970 --> 01:33:41.980 
我只是军官食堂的糕点师
I was only a pastry cook in the officers' mess.

